The strange thing for me here is that I came to NS for some nation RPing, yes, BUT I gravitated towards character RPs and development more often because for one, PG13, and because that's just my thing.

Fun fact: Clarissa was already a concept since 2014, a good year before Valentine Z came to be, let alone with Factbooks.

Another Fun Fact: The Sixty came to be because of my love for 60 as a number. There are technically 61 people in there but that was a later addition. I have a few others around in other nations, bumping up to 80, and then to 100-110 if I counted NS Sports characters.

If my favorite number is 420, there would be 420 characters.
